dct_title_s: Insurance maps of Trenton, Mercer Co., New Jersey (Sheet 27) (Sheet 27)
dct_description_sm: Title from title sheet. Includes location map, key, streets and specials index, and text. Includes maps of Morrisville, Bucks Co., Pa.; Lawrenceville School, and Hamilton Square, Mercer Co., N.J. on sheet 42. Oriented with the north to the upper left.
